1440
01:26:01.807 --> 01:26:05.083
which he had hairspray. something like that.
and it just...

1441
01:26:23.287 --> 01:26:27.565
After the accident. Michael had
to go through a horrific experience

1442
01:26:27.647 --> 01:26:29.319
to repair his scalp.

1443
01:26:29.527 --> 01:26:33.236
It was a form of tissue expansion
known as ballooning.

1444
01:26:35.527 --> 01:26:37.802
This procedure is often used on the scalp

1445
01:26:37.887 --> 01:26:40.162
Dr. Michael May FRCS - HAIR TRANSPLANT
SPECIALIST. THE WIMPOLE CLINIC

1446
01:26:40.247 --> 01:26:45.196
to treat burns. scarring.

1447
01:26:46.647 --> 01:26:48.558
This is done by the surgeon

1448
01:26:48.647 --> 01:26:53.960
inserting a plastic balloon
underneath the skin

1449
01:26:54.047 --> 01:26:58.962
and. over a period of time.
increasing the volume of the balloon.

1450
01:26:59.727 --> 01:27:02.878
and therefore. stretching the skin above.

1451
01:27:05.567 --> 01:27:07.159
The surgeons.

1452
01:27:07.327 --> 01:27:08.999
almost like drawing a curtain.

1453
01:27:09.087 --> 01:27:13.365
bring the normal tissue
over that area of scalp

1454
01:27:14.007 --> 01:27:16.885
and fill in the scarred area.

1455
01:27:20.207 --> 01:27:22.596
I actually spoke to Dr Steven Hoefflin.

1456
01:27:22.687 --> 01:27:27.158
who did the first ballooning procedure
on Michael after the Pepsi incident.

1457
01:27:27.247 --> 01:27:28.919
And he explained to me

1458
01:27:29.007 --> 01:27:33.444
Michael continued
to do the ballooning procedure

1459
01:27:33.527 --> 01:27:36.200
with different doctors. throughout his career.

1460
01:27:37.047 --> 01:27:39.242
It was quite painful. you can imagine.

1461
01:27:39.327 --> 01:27:45.118
If a large balloon of saline
is placed beneath the skin.

1462
01:27:45.207 --> 01:27:49.086
is blown up to perhaps 1000 cc of fluid.

1463
01:27:49.167 --> 01:27:52.364
it causes quite a large amount of discomfort.

1464
01:27:54.487 --> 01:27:56.239
I think after he got burnt.

1465
01:27:56.327 --> 01:27:59.399
that was the first time
he was exposed to strong pain medicine.

1466
01:27:59.487 --> 01:28:02.399
because he did have a lot of pain in that spot
