1512
01:30:35.967 --> 01:30:40.199
Bless his heart.
he financed a recording session for me.

1513
01:30:40.807 --> 01:30:43.605
He was a very giving person. Michael.

1514
01:30:44.367 --> 01:30:48.599
And very funny
