1534
01:32:16.327 --> 01:32:18.318
and I don't wanna cause any problems.

1535
01:32:18.887 --> 01:32:21.355
So we sat down very quickly.
within a few hours.

1536
01:32:21.447 --> 01:32:24.519
and we hammered out a deal.
which I think is fair to all of us.

1537
01:32:24.767 --> 01:32:26.598
And that's the story about This Is lt.

1538
01:32:30.527 --> 01:32:34.156
In 1990. I was producing
the American Cinema Awards.

1539
01:32:34.327 --> 01:32:37.285
which honoured legendary stars
of the cinema.

1540
01:32:37.367 --> 01:32:39.676
