washed down the drain.

2147
02:08:01.447 --> 02:08:03.483
I don't know how he coped.

2148
02:08:03.567 --> 02:08:05.762
Most people would've taken
a gun to their head.

2149
02:08:06.007 --> 02:08:09.204
His frame of mind was very. very fragile.

2150
02:08:10.007 --> 02:08:12.157
and I was concerned for him.

2151
02:08:12.327 --> 02:08:15.637
He was very worried
about his children and his mother

2152
02:08:15.727 --> 02:08:17.558
and what people would think.

2153
02:08:17.647 --> 02:08:19.239
The first day
of Gavin's testimony.

2154
02:08:19.327 --> 02:08:21.204
Michael shows up and he's in pyjamas.

2155
02:08:21.327 --> 02:08:23.522
and he looked like
he was in really bad shape.

2156
02:08:23.607 --> 02:08:26.599
And they actually. they had to. like.
help him into the courtroom.

2157
02:08:26.687 --> 02:08:30.123
From that moment on.
everything started to get really awful.

2158
02:08:30.367 --> 02:08:34.440
You started seeing Michael coming
