"You're a free man."

2192
02:11:24.687 --> 02:11:27.360
I could read his lips. 'cause I was so close.

2193
02:11:27.687 --> 02:11:29.996
And Michael still didn't get it.

2194
02:11:31.567 --> 02:11:33.239
You felt like it was a triumphant moment

2195
