to just walk amongst everyday people.

2225
02:13:29.327 --> 02:13:31.841
This was the first artist
that I'd been associated with.

2226
02:13:31.927 --> 02:13:32.916
Kenny Gamble & Leon Huff

2227
02:13:33.007 --> 02:13:34.235
PRODUCERS I SONGWRITERS.
PHILADELPHIA INT. RECORDS

2228
02:13:34.327 --> 02:13:35.555
and the only artist
