2235
02:14:09.487 --> 02:14:10.476
Martha Reeves
ARTIST. MOTOWN RECORDS

2236
02:14:10.567 --> 02:14:12.319
It's kind of hard being a king.

2237
02:14:12.407 --> 02:14:14.602
You can get out of sorts.

2238
02:14:16.327 --> 02:14:22.084
I think he. kind of. like. isolated himself
