02:14:31.247 --> 02:14:32.441
Billy Davis. Jr.
SINGER. '5th DIMENSION'

2242
02:14:32.527 --> 02:14:35.087
to give you an honest answer.
an honest opinion.

2243
02:14:35.167 --> 02:14:37.522
Joseph would always tell him.
"Michael. watch your people.

2244
02:14:37.607 --> 02:14:38.722
"Michael. watch your people."

2245
02:14:38.807 --> 02:14:41.844
He said. "I trust my people.
My people are good people."

2246
02:14:41.967 --> 02:14:44.765
But that's not the case.

2247
02:14:44.847 --> 02:14:45.836
