2303
02:17:45.447 --> 02:17:47.915
from as far back as I can remember.

2304
02:17:48.167 --> 02:17:50.123
Michael Jackson did have a problem.

2305
02:17:50.207 --> 02:17:52.084
Do I believe he was an addict?

2306
02:17:52.167 --> 02:17:55.159
No. I don't believe Michael Jackson
was a drug addict.

